model_explanation: S1 says the only thing Bill received from Sam was bananas, so he could not also have received grapes.
S1 says Mary is the only person who got apples, so Ellen could not also have received apples.
S1 restricts what Sue received, not what Tom received. Tom getting apples is neither entailed nor ruled out.
S1 says Bill is the only person who got grapes, but it says nothing about whether Bill got oranges.
S1 limits who received apples, not whether Bill received bananas.
S1 limits who received apples, not whether Sue received bananas.
if only Ellen got oranges, then Tom did not get oranges.
if only Tom got apples, then Mary did not get apples.
S1 restricts what Tom received, not whether Bill received apples.
S1 restricts what Sue received, not whether Tom received bananas.
